{"tid":2479643,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「連燈力」基金 呂布軍第二十九次股東大會，再敗SQQQ，麵神無助取勝...","createTime":"2021-04-08T03:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T03:05:21.000Z","uid":149018,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ed67ff41855631404feea34e6c1e07f2ee5c950","tid":2479643,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T03:02:01.000Z","msg":"「連燈力」基金 第二十八次軍議結算<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS2koxB9xZpgyGn1Gy8qWaK9NqaVuUMrZkrvQ2bD4r38j?filename=c2RrHNH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2RrHNH.png&h=a8f12768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVTgZ8CpnK4VEMniCwZi6to6vGVvanmNPDfME3XMPJPLZ?filename=uSCRTUn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSCRTUn.png&h=d8dbab36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZWB3mGtG1yzm6iEqFMizEtxaRuE2v3aoJ5Ls2Ti8idvf?filename=OEO18d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEO18d4.png&h=4f932ec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTrLN2HnUe4fnoYS2RS7A1WD8wF17aRuJEx7pEUGuXZxx?filename=NpHRSP3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpHRSP3.png&h=257bef7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"red\">681.13</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">31.89</span>%<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」基金 第二十九波操作意見收集<br />\n<br />\n「連燈力」呂布軍成立只為了股東日日有燒賣食，穩健投資，為燒賣ETF進發。<br />\n<br />\n一軍為短期戰線Daytrade陷陣營，二軍為呂布親領赤兔部隊留守主城。<br />\n請諸將及軍師團提議陷陣營進攻方向．<br />\n<br />\n1. 本次軍議操作為ALL IN制， 收集此帖巴打軍師將領意見<br />\n2. 收集軍師兵士們之股票後奉先設下點將台再以精明眼光買入。<br />\n3. 一軍買入時間預計為盤前16:00-18:00。<br />\n4. 二軍赤兔隊現正駐軍RBLX、FOXA、T，情況平淡。<br />\n5. 一軍陷陣營賣出時機分為&darr;<br />\na. 到達預計賣出時間為盤前21:00、開市緊急調動或盤後07:45<br />\nb. 增幅到達7%將立即設下5%止蝕位保存勝仗<br />\nc. 10%止賺及止蝕位。<br />\n6. 若陷陣營該次結算資金增長5% 隨機選中買入股票巴打派發Payme燒賣一串<br />\n7. 呂布將保留最終決定權，以上時機有機會皆為浮雲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYF8CYZdgnU2H7XkzghXoDmFVQLdkDD3Er92aqfVyg8g9?filename=4UR2XWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UR2XWx.jpg&h=9062ad7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2430824/page/1</a><br />\n第二十八次股東大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2478319/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2478319/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n呂布誤信奸臣9up，武力100 智力65操盤，請絕對相信本將軍判斷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTmEvyArwutJ6QAZrggGrFMR4o1vfe6D1oeEPxxG7YD4s?filename=9AtxDop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AtxDop.jpg&h=eb533600&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3aded7110b501acf050078540bdd77f118f92ec6","tid":2479643,"uid":14480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T03:03:35.000Z","msg":"PLD / UNH"},{"pid":"a3a8534bff132868e579000646be1a9d653bcb52","tid":2479643,"uid":21634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"奉先將軍投降吧啦"},{"pid":"13f048a01beaf2a8347e283f116ef17e2f576722","tid":2479643,"uid":201303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T03:03:54.000Z","msg":"今晚買返tcehy <br />\n嚟返個大反彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c138cf9675aa98de03b1a81136ee793d27f950c3","tid":2479643,"uid":69603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T03:04:06.000Z","msg":"輸多過贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79d6884b9b0dddb9dbe49ddf3f220a0f506005f","tid":2479643,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a8534bff132868e579000646be1a9d653bcb52","tid":2479643,"uid":21634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"奉先將軍投降吧啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"股票呢家野有無可能輸到得返1蚊"},{"pid":"24cc5e7c40f89aa684216220a99119411fd9ce85","tid"